author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how even YouTube Premium is now shuffling more ads, making it harder for users to legitimately escape the amount of ads they face. This is in line with most subscription services and honestly it's all becoming so tiring trying to navigate our content without any interruptions. Thanks for watching!

title: YouTube Premium Now Has Ads...
